      "beast_baseline": "i tried adding the 10px margin top but it didnt really work, the overlap is still there on my iphone. actually it's even worse, like the title is just completely buried behind the image now. do i need to use a media query or something to handle the mobile view specifically? maybe i should change the z-index or something too?",
