      "content": "thanks, the z-index helped the title show up but now the spacing is just super wonky. the image is squished and it looks like the whole layout is just breaking apart. it feels like the elements are just fighting each other for space instead of following the layout i set. is there a way to make the container more stable so they don't just crash into each other on small screens?",
